                                       "The item declaration, if found.")
                                     (item-ss vl-scopestack-p
                                              "The scopestack for the context
                                               in which the item was declared."))
                        (b* (((mv item context-ss pkg-name)
                              (vl-scopestack-find-item/context name ss))
